law.text:
As used in KRS 148.560 to 148.569, unless the context indicates otherwise:
"Authority" means the Appalachian/Kentucky Artisans Gateway Center Authority;
"Board" means the board of directors of the Appalachian/Kentucky Artisans Gateway Center Authority; and
"Center" means the Appalachian/Kentucky Artisans Gateway Center.
law.history: Created 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 22, sec. 1, effective July 14, 2000.
